      <title>新西兰央行维持利率不变，表示政策需要在一段时间内保持紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/nz-central-bank-holds-rates-says-policy-needs-stay-tight-while-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行周三将现金利率稳定在5.5%，重申之前的加息有助于抑制物价，但表示政策需要在一段时间内保持限制性，以使通胀低于目标区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/nz-central-bank-holds-rates-says-policy-needs-stay-tight-while-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚一月份通胀率维持在两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-inflation-holds-two-year-low-jan-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1月份澳大利亚消费者价格通胀保持在两年来的低点，打破了上涨的预期，并强化了市场预期利率不需要进一步提高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-inflation-holds-two-year-low-jan-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:17:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>领取补贴大米的长队凸显了印度尼西亚穷人的困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sprawling-queues-subsidised-rice-highlight-plight-indonesias-poor-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[午后的阳光下，数十名印度尼西亚人（其中大部分是女性）排着蜿蜒的队列购买一袋袋补贴大米，他们的手臂伸进金属门去抢门票，以确保他们有一个购买的位置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sprawling-queues-subsidised-rice-highlight-plight-indonesias-poor-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾总统称中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”，但不会阻止菲律宾保卫其海洋领土和保护其渔民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华纳兄弟探索频道计划关闭新西兰电视新闻提供商</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/warner-bros-discovery-plans-close-new-zealand-tv-news-provider-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰两家免费电视网络之一周三表示，拟从 6 月 30 日起关闭其新闻编辑室业务、电视新闻广播和网站，最多损失 200 个媒体工作岗位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/warner-bros-discovery-plans-close-new-zealand-tv-news-provider-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国敦促最大核国家谈判“不首先使用”条约</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-define-roadmap-exempt-non-nuclear-states-nuclear-threat-state-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部军控司表示，拥有最大核武库的国家应谈判签署互不首先使用核武器条约或就此发表政治声明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-define-roadmap-exempt-non-nuclear-states-nuclear-threat-state-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:14:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伍德赛德能源公司与韩国签署长期液化天然气供应协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/woodside-energy-inks-lng-supply-deal-with-south-korea-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚石油和天然气公司伍德赛德能源公司周三表示，伍德赛德能源公司已与韩国国有天然气公司韩国天然气公司签署了一项为期十多年的液化天然气（LNG）供应协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/woodside-energy-inks-lng-supply-deal-with-south-korea-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:48:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>兄弟姐妹帮助中国比亚迪在泰国电动汽车市场抢占先机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/siblings-help-chinas-byd-grab-early-lead-thai-ev-market-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年多前，比亚迪作为这家中国电动汽车制造商在泰国的唯一全国经销商推出后，Pratarnwong 和 Pratarnporn Phornprapha 兄弟姐妹被迫频繁撕毁商业计划，因为销量不断飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/siblings-help-chinas-byd-grab-early-lead-thai-ev-market-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:05:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚因高温和丛林大火威胁，数千人被告知逃离家园</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-told-flee-homes-australia-amid-heat-spike-bushfire-threat-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，澳大利亚东南部数万名居民被告知撤离，因为当局表示，强烈的热浪可能会进一步蔓延维多利亚州的大规模丛林大火，该州面临四年来最糟糕的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-told-flee-homes-australia-amid-heat-spike-bushfire-threat-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
